22
00:01:54,219 --> 00:01:56,000
I still want to be with everyone here.

23
00:01:56,909 --> 00:01:58,000
Besides,

24
00:01:59,469 --> 00:02:01,930
I haven’t found you your first love yet.

25
00:02:04,670 --> 00:02:06,329
I was scared you were going to leave us.

26
00:02:07,390 --> 00:02:08,840
Do you know how stressed out I was?

27
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:10,060
That’s why I would even sleep with you.

28
